{"tid":200002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2030年打通地殼 日本宣布鑽探地幔計劃","createTime":"2017-04-13T15:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T16:59:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"627dc6ba87837d2c60d76aa23aff382e123f9f9d","tid":200002,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net/images/2017/04/12/14920079546711wwc1EK0cGV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net%2Fimages%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F14920079546711wwc1EK0cGV.jpg&h=21e613fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了外太空是人類要探索之處，許多科學家認為地底研究比太空還要更困難，目前還無法鑽探到地球核心探索地球內部，但日本科學家宣布，將在2030年用日本最大的地質鑽探船「地球號」，鑽探到位在地殼和地核之間的地幔，至少鑽探10公里深以上，可能有助預測地震，和解密地球內是否還有其他文明存在。<br />\n <br />\n電影敘述地心停止轉動，結果一群科學家組成救援小組，坐地下飛船抵達地心，雖然按照目前人類科技不可能鑽探到地心，但日本海洋與地球科學技術機構科學家宣布，他們將在2030年鑽入位在地球內核、外核和地殼之間的地球地幔。如果成功，將是人類史上第一。<br />\n <br />\n根據CNN報導，研究團隊鑽探到地幔，將使用日本最大的地質鑽探船「地球號」，目前選定了3個鑽探地點是夏威夷、哥斯大黎加和墨西哥的太平洋海域，他們必須鑽過平均4公里深的海和6公里厚的海底地殼，至少鑽探10公里以上才會來到地幔上層，而研究地幔可能有助預測地震，這也是地震頻繁的日本要鑽探地幔的原因。<br />\n <br />\n不過，也有人指出，成功鑽探地球內部將解密地球內是否還有其他文明存在。甚至關於地球是空心的論述也從未停止過，1818年美國人「小約翰西蒙」提出「地球中空說」，他也是最著名的地球空洞說支持者，甚至在他遊說下，美國進行了到北極探索，地球空洞的計畫。但鑽探地幔最受主流科學家接受的還是，這將獲得更多岩石樣本，幫助人類理解地震和生命起源。而日本團隊成功鑽探地幔也將真正創造歷史，並且解決許多謎團。"},{"pid":"cb66765809c396ddbcb7dbc45712cd38d5b3c9f3","tid":200002,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:20:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=59096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D59096&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c5d61de5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=59096</a>"},{"pid":"14c771444c465dfd5885335358d857bedb0977ca","tid":200002,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"默示錄擊 一兆份之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b6a01a359d493cc5e0bbd75a0d4d48a3bf276c","tid":200002,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602dcc9a8fef39225f86a213414a89b751d6d3b2","tid":200002,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"地球空洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea088e4ac616541fa9b90190ad248fee03ae135f","tid":200002,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"問下理科撚，地幔係咪溶岩？"},{"pid":"54039aaed98b4ba9bee93e210d5a16b726558729","tid":200002,"uid":62443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問下理科撚，地幔係咪溶岩？</blockquote><br />\n上文都話重未有人探測到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f101cb81174a5d034f82df72233dc2f9014daae","tid":200002,"uid":25316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問下理科撚，地幔係咪溶岩？</blockquote><br />\n上文都話重未有人探測到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熔岩應該係subduction of plate 然後熔左之後嘅產物<br />\n<br />\n利申: 9 up"},{"pid":"e9cf7f2c562f08f71daea2bb32e5cd756065bd9d","tid":200002,"uid":39800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:04:15.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n諗起以前有套戲 攞核彈黎炸返郁個地核 等地球可以繼續自轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821c92895c365dc0f64c80014d44dfd9cf540ffc","tid":200002,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm<br />\n諗起以前有套戲 攞核彈黎炸返郁個地核 等地球可以繼續自轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵幾條友坐架類似火車落地底果套？"},{"pid":"35ac694b74eea44d9f22f915eae6a75af46b1bfb","tid":200002,"uid":37935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Lm<br />\n諗起以前有套戲 攞核彈黎炸返郁個地核 等地球可以繼續自轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵幾條友坐架類似火車落地底果套？</blockquote><br />\nThe core"},{"pid":"330b6761ec07cdd82c3342f4f64b31c692b70e75","tid":200002,"uid":60366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T17:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問下理科撚，地幔係咪溶岩？</blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n流左出地面既先係溶岩(lava)<br />\n重係地殻入面既叫岩漿(magma)<br />\n<br />\n至於地幔(mantle), 有成二, 三千公里厚<br />\n依家日本打算鑽入去果個只係上層地幔(Upper mantle)入面既最頂既最表皮個一忽, <br />\n由於依一層野係固體黎, <br />\n所以同地殼一樣, 地質學入面分類佢做岩石圈(Lithosphere)既一部份<br />\n<br />\n而我諗你想講既, 係地底入面有層軟淋淋, 好似溶岩既物體, <br />\n係地質學入面叫係做軟流層 (Asthenosphere), <br />\n簡單d講, 依一層亦都係上層地幔既一部份, <br />\n但係因為溫度高同地壓唔係話太大, 所以依一層既岩石一直係處於半融狀態<br />\nAsthenosphere通常係大概去到350km深, 不過係有d地方個Asthenosphere可能再厚多百幾km, 要視符果個地方既地層既岩石本身係乜構造<br />\n<br />\n而通常當個深度去到大概350km左右, <br />\n就算岩石既溫度依然係好高, 但係因為地壓愈黎愈大, 所以大部份岩石都保持左係固體狀態<br />\n由依一個深度開始既岩石層就會叫做Mesosphere, <br />\n通常Mesosphere包含左上層地幔既底部(軟&gt;硬既轉換層, 由深度350km- 深度700km) 同成個下層地幔(Lower mantle: 硬既岩石層), 一直延伸到落去地核為止<br />\n不過亦有人覺得由成個Mesosphere都係下層地幔<br />\n暫時未有結論<br />\n<br />\n而地震最深既震源就係位於350km- 700km依一個深度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係n年前既lecture notes入面搵到兩張幾易明既圖<br />\n你可以望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c16i650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc16i650.jpg&h=2be63546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fN2DR73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfN2DR73.jpg&h=04ba805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: n年前本身有major地質, 不過炒左其中一個core所以轉左做minor"},{"pid":"4170538aaf79ffc02c453455ddff203529683496","tid":200002,"uid":51602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問下理科撚，地幔係咪溶岩？</blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n流左出地面既先係溶岩(lava)<br />\n重係地殻入面既叫岩漿(magma)<br />\n<br />\n至於地幔(mantle), 有成二, 三千公里厚<br />\n依家日本打算鑽入去果個只係上層地幔(Upper mantle)入面既最頂既最表皮個一忽, <br />\n由於依一層野係固體黎, <br />\n所以同地殼一樣, 地質學入面分類佢做岩石圈(Lithosphere)既一部份<br />\n<br />\n而我諗你想講既, 係地底入面有層軟淋淋, 好似溶岩既物體, <br />\n係地質學入面叫係做軟流層 (Asthenosphere), <br />\n簡單d講, 依一層亦都係上層地幔既一部份, <br />\n但係因為溫度高同地壓唔係話太大, 所以依一層既岩石一直係處於半融狀態<br />\nAsthenosphere通常係大概去到350km深, 不過係有d地方個Asthenosphere可能再厚多百幾km, 要視符果個地方既地層既岩石本身係乜構造<br />\n<br />\n而通常當個深度去到大概350km左右, <br />\n就算岩石既溫度依然係好高, 但係因為地壓愈黎愈大, 所以大部份岩石都保持左係固體狀態<br />\n由依一個深度開始既岩石層就會叫做Mesosphere, <br />\n通常Mesosphere包含左上層地幔既底部(軟&gt;硬既轉換層, 由深度350km- 深度700km) 同成個下層地幔(Lower mantle: 硬既岩石層), 一直延伸到落去地核為止<br />\n不過亦有人覺得由成個Mesosphere都係下層地幔<br />\n暫時未有結論<br />\n<br />\n而地震最深既震源就係位於350km- 700km依一個深度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係n年前既lecture notes入面搵到兩張幾易明既圖<br />\n你可以望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c16i650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc16i650.jpg&h=2be63546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fN2DR73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfN2DR73.jpg&h=04ba805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: n年前本身有major地質, 不過炒左其中一個core所以轉左做minor</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8753826e7826d01339c69f143712ecf56dd57b24","tid":200002,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,