面叫係做軟流層 (Asthenosphere), <br />\n簡單d講, 依一層亦都係上層地幔既一部份, <br />\n但係因為溫度高同地壓唔係話太大, 所以依一層既岩石一直係處於半融狀態<br />\nAsthenosphere通常係大概去到350km深, 不過係有d地方個Asthenosphere可能再厚多百幾km, 要視符果個地方既地層既岩石本身係乜構造<br />\n<br />\n而通常當個深度去到大概350km左右, <br />\n就算岩石既溫度依然係好高, 但係因為地壓愈黎愈大, 所以大部份岩石都保持左係固體狀態<br />\n由依一個深度開始既岩石層就會叫做Mesosphere, <br />\n通常Mesosphere包含左上層地幔既底部(軟&gt;硬既轉換層, 由深度350km- 深度700km) 同成個下層地幔(Lower mantle: 硬既岩石層), 一直延伸到落去地核為止<br />\n不過亦有人覺得由成個Mesosphere都係下層地幔<br />\n暫時未有結論<br />\n<br />\n而地震最深既震源就係位於350km- 700km依一個深度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係n年前既lecture notes入面搵到兩張幾易明既圖<br />\n你可以望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c16i650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc16i650.jpg&h=2be63546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fN2DR73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfN2DR73.jpg&h=04ba805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: n年前本身有major地質, 不過炒左其中一個core所以轉左做minor</blockquote><br />\n其實呢啲係點計出黎 明明無人落過去睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94a2867485e795310fc4409a4f1ce731524476a","tid":200002,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:49:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23939c1f5513ef874914fb720422e06d2dc02860","tid":200002,"uid":42396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T19:01:35.000Z","msg":"地球係圓既<br />\n如果可以一路鑽鑽到頂既話會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8236995b0676c3447c2e93ca7be0df33f87a5de1","tid":200002,"uid":3083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T19:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得腸油嘅話實腸十枝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓上巴打真係高質，不過admin真係唔好搞咁多野啦，19腸油系統就算數巴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052c6f64556fd03971dbe40483ba52bb8436ba22","tid":200002,"uid":3488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T19:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地球係圓既<br />\n如果可以一路鑽鑽到頂既話會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲下會唔會條通道去地球另一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6b8e6e4616dd061541a944f54b74466a46bc90","tid":200002,"uid":42396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T19:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地球係圓既<br />\n如果可以一路鑽鑽到頂既話會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲下會唔會條通道去地球另一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果通去另一邊，咁究竟係向下鑽緊定向上鑽緊"},{"pid":"676375229e4842471125f2cb4f4e8def1993ae22","tid":200002,"uid":19643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T19:36:37.000Z","msg":"我唔係好明鑽地最難地方係邊  壓力溫度？"},{"pid":"fecda80519161c126965fbd99fab2bffc8978d3b","tid":200002,"uid":56680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T19:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識天文地理既男人真係好有型</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我大學讀geology meteorology 無人咁講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43b3584afb5c62e4733e3bec7622e06cad7275a","tid":200002,"uid":16775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T19:43:07.000Z","msg":"白痴問下<br />\n如果依家先係第一次鑽個地底<br />\n咁地球內部構造個啲資料全部都係估同推理出黎？"},{"pid":"02568f1f6ce0f94191809e02e1fd5d53261440ed","tid":200002,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T19:57:58.000Z","msg":"諗起蘇聯鑽探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc32d7afae3a835fa84336d0ccb37317ed9d6b8","tid":200002,"uid":100272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T20:07:58.000Z","msg":"認真（如果你又係認），建議係咁問點解有人會「知道」地球內部嘅人。<br />\n如果你哋重得十一二歲，好值得追去讀下書先，中學有科學課會有講乜嘢係理論與實驗。<br />\n如果你有十四五歲，咁你又真心好學，返去努力讀書睇多少少學術書，網上亦有好多教育資源。然後先再睇返上面篇文寫乜，因為你閱讀理解都應該好有問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果你考緊/考咗/考過DSE/HKCEE/HKAL，你浪費咗香港大量教育資源。請好好咁認真努力工作報效返社會。<br />\n<br />\n如果係玩嘢問嘅，當睇唔到呢個post。"},{"pid":"c5ab4b58fc2fe51cdc67959bdddcd16a10608ce5","tid":200002,"uid":100272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T20:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真（如果你又係認<span style=\"color: red;\">真</span>），建議係咁問點解有人會「知道」地球內部嘅人。<br />\n如果你哋重得十一二歲，好值得<span style=\"color: red;\">返</span>去讀下書先，中學有科學課會講乜嘢係<strong>理論與實驗</strong>。<br />\n如果你有十四五歲，咁你又真心好學，返去努力讀書睇多少少學術書，網上亦有好多教育資源。然後先再睇返上面篇文寫乜，因為你閱讀理解都應該好有問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果你考緊/考咗/考過DSE/HKCEE/HKAL，你浪費咗香港大量教育資源。請好好咁認真努力工作報效返社會。<br />\n<br />\n如果係玩嘢問嘅，當睇唔到呢個post。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"56513c4e7eea1b3a6a6c6827fea4612865c466eb","tid":200002,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T20:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白痴問下<br />\n如果依家先係第一次鑽個地底<br />\n咁地球內部構造個啲資料全部都係估同推理出黎？</blockquote><br />\n咁就當然唔係鳩估啦<br />\n係用科學分析出黎<br />\n例如地球內部構造, 最初係由透過d乜s-wave, p-wave既震動波係地底傳送既速度推斷出黎, 依個中學都教過<br />\n而d上層地幔既minerals既成份啊, 個地壓幾大啊, 有時其實係地面d十幾廿億年既古老板塊到有跡可尋, 因為好多依d老板塊曾經沉過落去地幔到, 而地幔既溫度, 壓力同成份令依d老板塊變左質<br />\n<br />\n不過家下關於地球既地質理論啱得幾多成, 一日我地唔拆開個地球黎望, 一日我地都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c7977051255da1b1c345be7649a9f7fc773ba9","tid":200002,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T20:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識天文地理既男人真係好有型</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我大學讀geology meteorology 無人咁講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀Geology一d都唔型, 不過係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去d山卡啦地方Field trip個陣, 朝早一路睇風景, 一路搵rock specimens帶番屋企,<br />\n 一路做fieldwork, <br />\n夜晚一路睇星, 一路同fd吹水, 一路劈酒<br />\n係我人生最開心既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒左個core亦係我人生最大遦憾之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e204c1d62df452dd6d7cb3077042d02c4d15ff","tid":200002,"uid":14595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T20:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓上巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得腸油嘅話實腸十枝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓上巴打真係高質，不過admin真係唔好搞咁多野啦，19腸油系統就算數巴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真正高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c53a41744026102c93a985d9f2a2fd06dcc4067","tid":200002,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T20:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>白痴問下<br />\n如果依家先係第一次鑽個地底<br />\n咁地球內部構造個啲資料全部都係估同推理出黎？</blockquote><br />\n咁就當然唔係鳩估啦<br />\n係用科學分析出黎<br />\n例如地球內部構造, 最初係由透過d乜s-wave, p-wave既震動波係地底傳送既速度推斷出黎, 依個中學都教過<br />\n而d上層地幔既minerals既成份啊, 個地壓幾大啊, 有時其實係地面d十幾廿億年既古老板塊到有跡可尋, 因為好多依d老板塊曾經沉過落去地幔到, 而地幔既溫度, 壓力同成份令依d老板塊變左質<br />\n<br />\n不過家下關於地球既地質理論啱得幾多成, 一日我地唔拆開個地球黎望, 一日我地都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nArchaeologist 挖淺啲 geologist 挖深啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a62eda9aeda76c0e7585d9f3484257f0f85d710","tid":200002,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T20:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>白痴問下<br />\n如果依家先係第一次鑽個地底<br />\n咁地球內部構造個啲資料全部都係估同推理出黎？</blockquote><br />\n咁就當然唔係鳩估啦<br />\n係用科學分析出黎<br />\n例如地球內部構造, 最初係由透過d乜s-wave, p-wave既震動波係地底傳送既速度推斷出黎, 依個中學都教過<br />\n而d上層地幔既minerals既成份啊, 個地壓幾大啊, 有時其實係地面d十幾廿億年既古老板塊到有跡可尋, 因為好多依d老板塊曾經沉過落去地幔到, 而地幔既溫度, 壓力同成份令依d老板塊變左質<br />\n<br />\n不過家下關於地球既地質理論啱得幾多成, 一日我地唔拆開個地球黎望, 一日我地都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nArchaeologist 挖淺啲 geologist 挖深啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我major Archaeology, minor Geology<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f347db237d38bf189d7d452413423898746275f5","tid":200002,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T21:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地球空洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地心吸引已經足以證明不是空洞"},{"pid":"001c41a4f4bbace8a7dbd327178de339c514dd93","tid":200002,"uid":16239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T21:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>白痴問下<br />\n如果依家先係第一次鑽個地底<br />\n咁地球內部構造個啲資料全部都係估同推理出黎？</blockquote><br />\n咁就當然唔係鳩估啦<br />\n係用科學分析出黎<br />\n例如地球內部構造, 最初係由透過d乜s-wave, p-wave既震動波係地底傳送既速度推斷出黎, 依個中學都教過<br />\n而d上層地幔既minerals既成份啊, 個地壓幾大啊, 有時其實係地面d十幾廿億年既古老板塊到有跡可尋, 因為好多依d老板塊曾經沉過落去地幔到, 而地幔既溫度, 壓力同成份令依d老板塊變左質<br />\n<br />\n不過家下關於地球既地質理論啱得幾多成, 一日我地唔拆開個地球黎望, 一日我地都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nArchaeologist 挖淺啲 geologist 挖深啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我major Archaeology, minor Geology<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手在民間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3358389707f96bc6b39e1cc44fd69613b1264713","tid":200002,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T21:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa20d3a60364d9a552d8f2b3cf850194d7b02f10","tid":200002,"uid":3739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T21:55:59.000Z","msg":"之前蘇聯都好似鑽探過<br />\n話鑽探入去後聽到好多人慘叫 好似18層地獄咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就冇再探落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2dc372f2be65b9894a105e724284c3b9bd13a0","tid":200002,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T22:11:49.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9082ae84fc695a5d680888d131256606eb9ea72b","tid":200002,"uid":89402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T22:21:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下你地一齊聯署簽名去日本叫佢停止呢個鑽探計！</span></span><br />\n是咁的 小弟天生有啲預視能力 假如佢地再鑽既話會激嬲地下下面啲地底人 本身佢地遵守幾百年前與地面人互不侵犯既協定 但係無知既我地再咁樣騷擾佢地必然會引起一場大災難 我預見到既係地球將會一片混亂 人類將會滅絕 <br />\n<br />\n求下你地我唔想<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">地球大爆炸呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"072a1e9811372c779a39af0bd5ffe51fb97d0639","tid":200002,"uid":100272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T22:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識天文地理既男人真係好有型</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我大學讀geology meteorology 無人咁講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀Geology一d都唔型, 不過係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去d山卡啦地方Field trip個陣, 朝早一路睇風景, 一路搵rock specimens帶番屋企,<br />\n 一路做fieldwork, <br />\n夜晚一路睇星, 一路同fd吹水, 一路劈酒<br />\n係我人生最開心既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒左個core亦係我人生最大遦憾之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得正，中學時曾經最鍾意Geography地質堂。"},{"pid":"ac38443af1efab5949e827e4dbebc3f9a75bf768","tid":200002,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T22:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問下理科撚，地幔係咪溶岩？</blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n流左出地面既先係溶岩(lava)<br />\n重係地殻入面既叫岩漿(magma)<br />\n<br />\n至於地幔(mantle), 有成二, 三千公里厚<br />\n依家日本打算鑽入去果個只係上層地幔(Upper mantle)入面既最頂既最表皮個一忽, <br />\n由於依一層野係固體黎, <br />\n所以同地殼一樣, 地質學入面分類佢做岩石圈(Lithosphere)既一部份<br />\n<br />\n而我諗你想講既, 係地底入面有層軟淋淋, 好似溶岩既物體, <br />\n係地質學入面叫係做軟流層 (Asthenosphere), <br />\n簡單d講, 依一層亦都係上層地幔既一部份, <br />\n但係因為溫度高同地壓唔係話太大, 所以依一層既岩石一直係處於半融狀態<br />\nAsthenosphere通常係大概去到350km深, 不過係有d地方個Asthenosphere可能再厚多百幾km, 要視符果個地方既地層既岩石本身係乜構造<br />\n<br />\n而通常當個深度去到大概350km左右, <br />\n就算岩石既溫度依然係好高, 但係因為地壓愈黎愈大, 所以大部份岩石都保持左係固體狀態<br />\n由依一個深度開始既岩石層就會叫做Mesosphere, <br />\n通常Mesosphere包含左上層地幔既底部(軟&gt;硬既轉換層, 由深度350km- 深度700km) 同成個下層地幔(Lower mantle: 硬既岩石層), 一直延伸到落去地核為止<br />\n不過亦有人覺得由成個Mesosphere都係下層地幔<br />\n暫時未有結論<br />\n<br />\n而地震最深既震源就係位於350km- 700km依一個深度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係n年前既lecture notes入面搵到兩張幾易明既圖<br />\n你可以望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c16i650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc16i650.jpg&h=2be63546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fN2DR73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfN2DR73.jpg&h=04ba805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: n年前本身有major地質, 不過炒左其中一個core所以轉左做minor</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b5f37302b7f47d6a9e38ca82b5fd1d5b4cfd47","tid":200002,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T22:58:19.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a1f8c06ab5954f4eed3299a323edf3de1a40c511","tid":200002,"uid":3739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T23:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下你地一齊聯署簽名去日本叫佢停止呢個鑽探計！</span></span><br />\n是咁的 小弟天生有啲預視能力 假如佢地再鑽既話會激嬲地下下面啲地底人 本身佢地遵守幾百年前與地面人互不侵犯既協定 但係無知既我地再咁樣騷擾佢地必然會引起一場大災難 我預見到既係地球將會一片混亂 人類將會滅絕 <br />\n<br />\n求下你地我唔想<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">地球大爆炸呀！</span></span></blockquote><br />\n你見到既野即係將來會發生？<br />\n如果阻止到 將來就唔會發生你就睇唔到<br />\n我信有地底人 亦信你有預視能力 但都要班19科學家信先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a21f76b1e3ca0e678705f3108fe46a8d2edc0c","tid":200002,"uid":75914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T23:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>白痴問下<br />\n如果依家先係第一次鑽個地底<br />\n咁地球內部構造個啲資料全部都係估同推理出黎？</blockquote><br />\n咁就當然唔係鳩估啦<br />\n係用科學分析出黎<br />\n例如地球內部構造, 最初係由透過d乜s-wave, p-wave既震動波係地底傳送既速度推斷出黎, 依個中學都教過<br />\n而d上層地幔既minerals既成份啊, 個地壓幾大啊, 有時其實係地面d十幾廿億年既古老板塊到有跡可尋, 因為好多依d老板塊曾經沉過落去地幔到, 而地幔既溫度, 壓力同成份令依d老板塊變左質<br />\n<br />\n不過家下關於地球既地質理論啱得幾多成, 一日我地唔拆開個地球黎望, 一日我地都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nArchaeologist 挖淺啲 geologist 挖深啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我major Archaeology, minor Geology<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打讀呢科有咩岀路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb66c68488f3af5e401e050fcc02c3e1677d197","tid":200002,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T23:29:41.000Z","msg":"地心有人住架"},{"pid":"b819de3789549236b3f0c2e5e21710b123796d48","tid":200002,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:22:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e19e5859f5c24d334ab900f39631170d7726674","tid":200002,"uid":11521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得當年美蘇冷戰 蘇聯為左向美國證明自己實力所以想轉地轉到地核 點知唔成功 不過鑽到咁上下好似聽到有人慘叫既聲音 好似係地獄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後係因為好似潮流玩飛去太空所以先轉左。因為話經濟價值採探到咁深都無乜意思， 所以就停左個計劃"},{"pid":"eb507726ea651d8dba2663775d1afa85381af1d3","tid":200002,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:37:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbcd39d568f077a746001c097953d1b7d5576af4","tid":200002,"uid":2216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識天文地理既男人真係好有型</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我大學讀geology meteorology 無人咁講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀Geology一d都唔型, 不過係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去d山卡啦地方Field trip個陣, 朝早一路睇風景, 一路搵rock specimens帶番屋企,<br />\n 一路做fieldwork, <br />\n夜晚一路睇星, 一路同fd吹水, 一路劈酒<br />\n係我人生最開心既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒左個core亦係我人生最大遦憾之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n介唔介意透露下係邊科咁難？<br />\n而家係咪做返呢方面嘅工作？"},{"pid":"f864a501c6125ac2f1e87d23c236eca355ffc68e","tid":200002,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我記得當年美蘇冷戰 蘇聯為左向美國證明自己實力所以想轉地轉到地核 點知唔成功 不過鑽到咁上下好似聽到有人慘叫既聲音 好似係地獄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後係因為好似潮流玩飛去太空所以先轉左。因為話經濟價值採探到咁深都無乜意思， 所以就停左個計劃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.tampereclub.ru/uploads/posts/2013-10/1382033104_eksperement-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tampereclub.ru%2Fuploads%2Fposts%2F2013-10%2F1382033104_eksperement-01.jpg&h=0292dcb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科拉超深井<br />\n事實係1989年成功鑽透12,262公尺<br />\n再運行至2008年先因為無錢放棄項目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講有地獄有慘叫不如去彩虹站搵下好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7951a3db8dd72e938d3d86079ea03f9c42f6de62","tid":200002,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>白痴問下<br />\n如果依家先係第一次鑽個地底<br />\n咁地球內部構造個啲資料全部都係估同推理出黎？</blockquote><br />\n咁就當然唔係鳩估啦<br />\n係用科學分析出黎<br />\n例如地球內部構造, 最初係由透過d乜s-wave, p-wave既震動波係地底傳送既速度推斷出黎, 依個中學都教過<br />\n而d上層地幔既minerals既成份啊, 個地壓幾大啊, 有時其實係地面d十幾廿億年既古老板塊到有跡可尋, 因為好多依d老板塊曾經沉過落去地幔到, 而地幔既溫度, 壓力同成份令依d老板塊變左質<br />\n<br />\n不過家下關於地球既地質理論啱得幾多成, 一日我地唔拆開個地球黎望, 一日我地都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nArchaeologist 挖淺啲 geologist 挖深啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我major Archaeology, minor Geology<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打好勁，知識方面唔洗講，表達能力亦好厲害，連我睇一次都由完全唔識變做即刻明晒，能夠將事物深入淺出先係高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4549a26f830089467964eb4c0a1eb578bad550","tid":200002,"uid":27017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真（如果你又係認<span style=\"color: red;\">真</span>），建議係咁問點解有人會「知道」地球內部嘅人。<br />\n如果你哋重得十一二歲，好值得<span style=\"color: red;\">返</span>去讀下書先，中學有科學課會講乜嘢係<strong>理論與實驗</strong>。<br />\n如果你有十四五歲，咁你又真心好學，返去努力讀書睇多少少學術書，網上亦有好多教育資源。然後先再睇返上面篇文寫乜，因為你閱讀理解都應該好有問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果你考緊/考咗/考過DSE/HKCEE/HKAL，你浪費咗香港大量教育資源。請好好咁認真努力工作報效返社會。<br />\n<br />\n如果係玩嘢問嘅，當睇唔到呢個post。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你好叻叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc6ada733590fe7b4ef14156425757e9cf8ef20","tid":200002,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下你地一齊聯署簽名去日本叫佢停止呢個鑽探計！</span></span><br />\n是咁的 小弟天生有啲預視能力 假如佢地再鑽既話會激嬲地下下面啲地底人 本身佢地遵守幾百年前與地面人互不侵犯既協定 但係無知既我地再咁樣騷擾佢地必然會引起一場大災難 我預見到既係地球將會一片混亂 人類將會滅絕 <br />\n<br />\n求下你地我唔想<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">地球大爆炸呀！</span></span></blockquote><br />\n你見到既野即係將來會發生？<br />\n如果阻止到 將來就唔會發生你就睇唔到<br />\n我信有地底人 亦信你有預視能力 但都要班19科學家信先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9996c376bf9c494af8143b17081e2e065787bc42","tid":200002,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:39:42.000Z","msg":"鑽到去地球另一面"},{"pid":"72887bd601fc51aebad4d77dae473d89d5947e7b","tid":200002,"uid":9217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:45:47.000Z","msg":"第一次覺得連登真係有高人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95db1ada6e14133b463e5af9fad4c8d2cc78e651","tid":200002,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:03:12.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4fa2ebb5c1858b4d7dd974cbd3be256dc80a3eae","tid":200002,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:13:54.000Z","msg":"其實依加對地球嘅了好多只係假設<br />\n就算板塊論都係未證實到<br />\n唔排除將來會有一套更完整論述推返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33254f24904d9523f91cfa2c5e1e7040b0179113","tid":200002,"uid":16406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真（如果你又係認<span style=\"color: red;\">真</span>），建議係咁問點解有人會「知道」地球內部嘅人。<br />\n如果你哋重得十一二歲，好值得<span style=\"color: red;\">返</span>去讀下書先，中學有科學課會講乜嘢係<strong>理論與實驗</strong>。<br />\n如果你有十四五歲，咁你又真心好學，返去努力讀書睇多少少學術書，網上亦有好多教育資源。然後先再睇返上面篇文寫乜，因為你閱讀理解都應該好有問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果你考緊/考咗/考過DSE/HKCEE/HKAL，你浪費咗香港大量教育資源。請好好咁認真努力工作報效返社會。<br />\n<br />\n如果係玩嘢問嘅，當睇唔到呢個post。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你好叻叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有潮文潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234aa1ddecd3f7ac981b692ba2b1db282c952cb3","tid":200002,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>地球係圓既<br />\n如果可以一路鑽鑽到頂既話會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲下會唔會條通道去地球另一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果通去另一邊，咁究竟係向下鑽緊定向上鑽緊</blockquote><br />\n中間開始倒返轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df7809b55a8c06e9d759f56ebe542a84f64a571","tid":200002,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"我比較想知，鑽過左地殼之後，果個位地壓應該會大減<br />\n咁果d因為高壓而keep到固體的岩漿，會唔會變返液體噴出黎，好似火山咁"},{"pid":"b74a23c8f1a3220e0222c553aca7216eb288b61e","tid":200002,"uid":38337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"日本可以發展全球化嘅地下鐵<br />\nbtw,比較想探索海洋嘅最深處"},{"pid":"2622e9ab0c1179e6532baa47965fcc8b4fbd29f3","tid":200002,"uid":11328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>問下理科撚，地幔係咪溶岩？</blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n流左出地面既先係溶岩(lava)<br />\n重係地殻入面既叫岩漿(magma)<br />\n<br />\n至於地幔(mantle), 有成二, 三千公里厚<br />\n依家日本打算鑽入去果個只係上層地幔(Upper mantle)入面既最頂既最表皮個一忽, <br />\n由於依一層野係固體黎, <br />\n所以同地殼一樣, 地質學入面分類佢做岩石圈(Lithosphere)既一部份<br />\n<br />\n而我諗你想講既, 係地底入面有層軟淋淋, 好似溶岩既物體, <br />\n係地質學入面叫係做軟流層 (Asthenosphere), <br />\n簡單d講, 依一層亦都係上層地幔既一部份, <br />\n但係因為溫度高同地壓唔係話太大, 所以依一層既岩石一直係處於半融狀態<br />\nAsthenosphere通常係大概去到350km深, 不過係有d地方個Asthenosphere可能再厚多百幾km, 要視符果個地方既地層既岩石本身係乜構造<br />\n<br />\n而通常當個深度去到大概350km左右, <br />\n就算岩石既溫度依然係好高, 但係因為地壓愈黎愈大, 所以大部份岩石都保持左係固體狀態<br />\n由依一個深度開始既岩石層就會叫做Mesosphere, <br />\n通常Mesosphere包含左上層地幔既底部(軟&gt;硬既轉換層, 由深度350km- 深度700km) 同成個下層地幔(Lower mantle: 硬既岩石層), 一直延伸到落去地核為止<br />\n不過亦有人覺得由成個Mesosphere都係下層地幔<br />\n暫時未有結論<br />\n<br />\n而地震最深既震源就係位於350km- 700km依一個深度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係n年前既lecture notes入面搵到兩張幾易明既圖<br />\n你可以望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c16i650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc16i650.jpg&h=2be63546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fN2DR73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfN2DR73.jpg&h=04ba805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: n年前本身有major地質, 不過炒左其中一個core所以轉左做minor</blockquote><br />\n其實呢啲係點計出黎 明明無人落過去睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n估嘅。</blockquote><br />\n係用聲納掃完，<br />\n再睇返掃完嘅物質大概嘅硬度去估，<br />\n其實咪又係估，<br />\n根本冇人知真正係點，所以一直有空心論之類嘅陰謀論，所以話唔定日本今次落一落地底會推翻d理論"},{"pid":"35607daca28e55cea43385e411799372292dda04","tid":200002,"uid":11328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起蘇聯鑽探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地獄之洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21ec9272dc5a5909d7c17dccaa30f97260b92ef","tid":200002,"uid":11328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><b